children.name: Compact Markdown Within certain views, the markdown type scale is decreased in order to more closely align copy with other UI components. Compact markdown is used for descriptions and comments on issue and merge request pages. Content written using markdown includes typography that contains fixed margins and increased line-heights to improve readability.
